* Instructions - 

** (0) Get OpenAL https://www.openal.org/downloads/

** (1) Get latest version of SOX
git clone git://git.code.sf.net/p/sox/code sox

** (2) Install SOX
brew install sox
or
http://sourceforge.net/projects/sox/files/sox/

** (3) Put Sox and OpenAL on your Environment PATH (Windows)

** (4) Convert sound file from wav to raw 
sox footsteps-4.wav -b 16 footsteps.raw channels 1 rate 44100

** (5) Compile with:
gcc -framework OpenAL -framework Cocoa -o footsteps footsteps.c (Mac?)
gcc -o footsteps footsteps.c -lopenal (Windows)

** (6) Run by typing:
./footsteps 